lyTime":"2021-01-29T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"信你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藉口都分析"},{"pid":"0c56dac7536b8c420c98c94462425f86995ab038","tid":2386352,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c529cbc3cf38acdc5270a2eb39ca6180d5aa8cb8","tid":2386352,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"854580673175a6b472fa5cf169818e93212ce980","tid":2386352,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"277ae22a2622cf95c9919ee9f093f9ff7141e93c","tid":2386352,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"有咩野令你心花怒放？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653c44ce7c6411295f21175066d51b7f9e4e4a15","tid":2386352,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e6a2e89893503f5384dbb2f8e31466f101103fe","tid":2386352,"uid":274161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOHA1jM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOHA1jM.jpg&h=4ce497d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"572eeeefa1d440c295d41d14879a013c922a25b5","tid":2386352,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3beb308c4f60053cc949ba70cd1df197af8fd9c7","tid":2386352,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"即係彈出彈入打閃避球<br />\n是旦搵人簽就當支持國安法<br />\n嗰排好似話簽個名拎口罩同防疫用品嗰啲野<br />\n真係廉價到"},{"pid":"7d4a56521f46d48f45f0e1ebcc2f21c9dd9106a8","tid":2386352,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"先講我唔認為佢會信<br />\n但佢信唔信跟本唔係重點<br />\n而係點解佢會引用"},{"pid":"37be6c33f2cd2009ea8185be8665701179dae556","tid":2386352,"uid":37111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"be2697c6c454bc4c670d396846bde9986a3b0327","tid":2386352,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"258be47566a7ea2ec40d73b9e9a6a184a7091fae","tid":2386352,"uid":2752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"重點係盤數俾人不停互相引用就變咗「真實」"}}